               <svg viewbox="0 0 14 14" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" class="awscc-u-cb-checkbox">
                <rect class="awscc-u-cb-checkbox-rect" x="0.5" y="0.5" rx="1.5" ry="1.5" width="13" height="13"></rect><polyline class="awscc-u-cb-checkbox-poly-line " points="2.5,7 6,10 11,3"></polyline>
               </svg></label>
             </div>
            </div><span class="awsccc-u-cb-text">Allowed</span>
           </div>
          </div>
         </div>
         <div id="awsccc-cs-l-container">
          <p><span>Blocking some types of cookies may impact your experience of our sites. You may review and change your choices at any time by clicking Cookie preferences in the footer of this site. We and selected third-parties use cookies or similar technologies as specified in the&nbsp;<a data-id="awsccc-cs-f-notice" href="https://aws.amazon.com/legal/cookies/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><span>AWS Cookie Notice<span aria-label="Opens in a new Window" role="img" class="awsccc-u-i-open-c">
