           <img class="highlight-image float-left" src="https://res.cdn.office.net/officehub/images/content/images/unauth-refresh/highlight-commercial-2-f143e5c2d2.png" alt="Desktop and mobile app screenshots representing the organizational components of Microsoft 365"> 
